in-bottom: 8px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;'>Project Description</label><textarea rows='4' placeholder='[Describe your project]' style='width: 100%; padding: 12px 15px; background: #0F0F0F; border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.3); color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 15px; font-family: DM Sans; resize: vertical;'></textarea></div><div style='margin-bottom: 25px;'><label style='display: block; font-size: 13px; color: #C8A96E; margin-bottom: 8px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;'>Best Time to Call</label><select style='width: 100%; padding: 12px 15px; background: #0F0F0F; border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.3); color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 15px; font-family: DM Sans;'><option>Select a time</option><option>Morning</option><option>Afternoon</option><option>Evening</option></select></div></form>"
